    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add your<strong> pork & beef mince </strong>to the dish and break it up with a wooden spoon</p><p>Peel and grate your <strong>garlic</strong></p><p>Add your <strong>tomato paste</strong>,<strong> grated garlic</strong> and a knob of <strong>butter </strong>to the dish and give everything a good mix up</p>",
      "order": 3,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-3-1695657740362-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
