            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add your<strong> chopped tomatoes</strong>, <strong>beef stock mix</strong>, <strong>balsamic vinegar </strong>and 650ml <span class=\"text-purple\">[850ml] </span><span class=\"text-danger\">[1.1L] </span><strong>boiled water </strong>and give everything a good mix up</p><p>Bring to the boil over a high heat, season generously with <strong>salt</strong> and<strong> pepper</strong>, then cover with a lid and put the dish in the oven for an initial 30 min – this is your<strong> pork & beef ragù</strong></p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-4-1695657744740-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-4-1695657744740-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-4-1695657744740-x700.jpg",
