          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-4-1695657744740-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-4-1695657744740-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>After 30 min, remove the<strong> pork & beef ragù</strong> from the oven</p><p>Break your <strong>spaghetti</strong> in half and add it to the dish, giving everything a good mix up to separate the strands</p><p>Return the dish to the oven and cook, covered, for a final 25 min or until the spaghetti is tender and the mince is cooked through (no pink meat!) – this is your<strong> all-in-one pork & beef ragù spaghetti</strong></p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
        "images": [
