      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the ragù is almost done, slice your <strong>tomato[es]</strong> finely and add to a bowl</p><p>Roughly tear <strong>half</strong> your<strong> basil leaves</strong> over the top (save the rest for later!)</p><p>Drizzle with <strong>olive oil</strong> and season with <strong>salt</strong> and <strong>pepper</strong> – this is your <strong>tomato & basil salad</strong></p>",
      "order": 7,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
